# The homepage is the documentation

    stable 003
   require dbus-glib udev
      opts --disable-gtk-doc
  category security
 attribute console
    source http://hal.freedesktop.org/releases/DeviceKit-$VERSION.tar.gz
      home http://hal.freedesktop.org/docs/DeviceKit/
  estimate 300
      desc 'a dbus frontend to udev
DeviceKit is an abstraction for enumerating devices
and listening to device events.
Any application on the system can access the
org.freedesktop.DeviceKit service via the system message bus.
On GNU/Linux, DeviceKit can be considered a simple D-Bus frontend to udev(7).'
